Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:31.51,KHJ_SUB,,0,0,0,,是能吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:33.76,KHJ_SUB,,0,0,0,,是观赏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.51,KHJ_SUB,,0,0,0,,嘉禄也很香
